{"word":"H5670 - עָבַט - ʻâbaṭ - aw-bat' - Borrow - கடன்வாங்கு","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>עָבַט"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>ʻâbaṭ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>aw-bat'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Borrow / கடன்வாங்கு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வாங்கு, கடன்வாங்கு, பிசகு, கடன்கொடு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to take a pledge, to give a pledge (for a debt)"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) to take a pledge, to give a pledge (for a debt)"},{"paragraph":"b) (Piel) to interchange"},{"paragraph":"c) (Hiphil) to cause to give a pledge"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>pawn</i>; causatively to <i>lend</i> (on security); figuratively to <i>entangle: - </i>borrow, break [ranks], fetch [a pledge], lend, X surely."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H5667 - עֲבֹוט - ʻăbôwṭ - ab-ote'/5667\">H5667</a>, <a href=\"#/H5670 - עָבַט - ʻâbaṭ - aw-bat'/5670\">H5670</a>, <a href=\"#/H5671 - עַבְטִיט - ʻabṭîyṭ - ab-teet'/5671\">H5671</a>"}]}